{"tid":1282962,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[求傾計] 好似講唔到野咁","createTime":"2019-07-03T16:36:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T18:41:05.000Z","uid":133103,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9ed686cdb3129161d5912b368cfc7a20d631eb33","tid":1282962,"uid":133103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:36:36.000Z","msg":"因為政治立場唔同 連日尼都避開同阿媽傾太多<br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記得第二位烈士走個日 我同我阿媽講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 又有一位 比香港政權逼死左<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 多9餘<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 香港人尼嫁 你點可以咁講野<br />\n佢冇理我<br />\n<br />\n今日 我媽有野想鬧我阿哥 鬧左一句 就話<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 香港啲年青人係咁 有錯又唔認<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 真係做咩 再努力都冇用 做人真係好難<br />\n忍唔住即刻喊左<br />\n<br />\n原本白色恐怖 加上不斷有企跳既消息 <br />\n個心已經梗住梗住<br />\n個人又要不斷發惡夢<br />\n想同人傾又覺得傾唔到 同男朋友又鬧交<br />\n身邊有朋友係哩個時候仲不斷吃喝玩樂 所以都冇意欲同佢地傾<br />\n<br />\n利申:唔會諗歪 唔想帶負能量 但好想打岀尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83dd21e17837cd677bae8d5ebccb27b3400c71c9","tid":1282962,"uid":157983,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:37:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aaa5221f4f9bc0e19b1f61548fbaecb1e18cea6a","tid":1282962,"uid":157983,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:38:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b5b87b90051a1c7482f8bea5ef683bf1306c4a0","tid":1282962,"uid":133103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T17:05:52.000Z","msg":"...."},{"pid":"7ff49b2874412db9dc797506cac87772c50111dc","tid":1282962,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T17:24:16.000Z","msg":"休息下, 放鬆下先啦, 小妹妹 ! <br />\n同家人朋友唔一定要講政治既野, 免相和氣 !"},{"pid":"ad19c3dd67dec0d52d134979d8548292db48009b","tid":1282962,"uid":133103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7ff49b2874412db9dc797506cac87772c50111dc","tid":1282962,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T17:24:16.000Z","msg":"休息下, 放鬆下先啦, 小妹妹 ! <br />\n同家人朋友唔一定要講政治既野, 免相和氣 !"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:25:27.000Z","msg":"我後來冇講 但佢每次一傾計就提起"},{"pid":"6edb967cb67935a5ed03dc15950da06f8e34e0b8","tid":1282962,"uid":133103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:26:23.000Z","msg":"多謝兩位陪我傾兩句"},{"pid":"17a710677f156b3887e5a0d832cd1383fd7e618e","tid":1282962,"uid":194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:38:45.000Z","msg":"試下上床戴耳機聽下歌,<br />\n放鬆下個人,<br />\n總會有啲人/事令到你好激氣,由其屋企人更什<br />\n無辦法,每個人諗法/立場都唔同<br />\n盡量唔好再同屋企人提起啦,<br />\n如果仲想講關於政治既話題,搵返岩嘴形既人講好啲<br />\n共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef4d34c58ae5ae834ec5f64fbc59612d4ee44fec","tid":1282962,"uid":254371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:41:05.000Z","msg":"出去行下，放鬆一下"}]}